
# Nova

Nova is Tyler's local AI assistant system.

## Goals
- Local AI assistant
- Project memory
- Morning briefings
- Home automation
- Voice interaction
- System monitoring
- Self-maintenance tools

## Current Stack
- Ubuntu/Linux AI PC
- Ollama
- Open WebUI
- Docker
- Home Assistant
- VS Code Remote SSH

## Philosophy
Nova's core memory, scripts, and configuration should remain portable and permanent.
External programs are replaceable modules.
EOF
